:"So what yet causes you to deny the Recompense?","words":[{"position":1,"ar":"فَمَا","fr":"Alors que","en":"Then what","tr":"famā","isWaqf":false},{"position":2,"ar":"يُكَذِّبُكَ","fr":"cause vous à nier","en":"causes you to deny","tr":"yukadhibuka","isWaqf":false},{"position":3,"ar":"بَعْدُ","fr":"après (ceci)","en":"after (this)","tr":"baʿdu","isWaqf":false},{"position":4,"ar":"بِٱلدِّينِ","fr":"le jugement","en":"the judgment","tr":"bil-dīni","isWaqf":false}]},{"ayah":8,"verseKey":"95:8","juz":30,"arabic":"أَلَيْسَ ٱللَّهُ بِأَحْكَمِ ٱلْحَـٰكِمِينَ","fr":"Allah n’est-Il pas le plus Sage des juges ?","en":"Is not Allāh the most just of judges?","words":[{"position":1,"ar":"أَلَيْسَ","fr":"Est non","en":"Is not","tr":"alaysa","isWaqf":false},{"position":2,"ar":"ٱللَّهُ","fr":"Allah","en":"Allah","tr":"l-lahu","isWaqf":false},{"position":3,"ar":"بِأَحْكَمِ","fr":"(le) Très Juste","en":"(the) Most Just","tr":"bi-aḥkami","isWaqf":false},{"position":4,"ar":"ٱلْحَـٰكِمِينَ","fr":"(de) le Juge","en":"(of) the Judges","tr":"l-ḥākimīna","isWaqf":false}]}]